title: Bug 121682: Exception throws when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map.
description: Exception is thrown when exporting data from the attached report.
OB: Upon attempting to export data from a table that contains a highlight or map, an exception is thrown.
EB: Exporting data from a table with a highlight or map should not result in any exceptions.
SR:
1. Open the attached report.
2. Navigate to a table that contains a highlight or map.
3. Attempt to export data from the table.
4. Observe the exception being thrown.
